@  ----
@  By Craig Forman
@  Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal </HL>
  <DD> <TIMEX3 functionInDocument="CREATION_TIME" temporalFunction="false" tid="t89" type="DATE" value="1989-10-31">10/31/89</TIMEX3> </DD>
